// 02_arithmetic.bund
// Stack-based arithmetic. Values accumulate on the stack;
// operators consume two values and push one result.

// Basic operations
3 4 +    println    // 7
10 3 -   println    // 7
6 7 *    println    // 42
84 2 /   println    // 42

// Operator precedence is execution order — no hidden rules
// (3 + 4) * 2  written as postfix:
3 4 + 2 * println   // 14

// 10 - (2 * 3)  written as postfix:
2 3 * 10 swap - println   // 4

// Floating-point arithmetic
2.0 float.sqrt println     // ~1.414...
float.Pi 2.0 / println     // ~1.5707... (π/2)
-5.0 float.abs println     // 5.0
9.0 float.cbrt println     // ~2.08...  (∛9)

// Integer vs float promotion
10 3 /    println           // 3  (integer division)
10.0 3.0 / println          // 3.333...  (float division)

// Bulk sum of all values on stack
1 2 3 4 5 *+ println        // 15
